      <title>Signa 债权人支持重组计划并承诺支付 30%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/signa-creditors-back-restructuring-plan-paying-out-30-on-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Signa Prime Selection AG 的债权人支持这家破产房地产公司有序出售数十亿欧元豪华房产的提议，启动了重组，预计将在两年内收回至少 30% 的资金。]]></description>
